    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/81407ab3ac69999ce5139169652fb25d.avif?t=1719328299\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong><i>&quot;Welcome to Knight Fall: Survive <u>Bosses</u> and Claim Victory at the Top!</i></strong> Every move is a challenge as you jump through dangerous lands, battling tough <u>bosses</u> along the way. Be careful; one wrong move could end your journey. Will you beat the horrors or fall to the <u>bosses</u> on your daring quest?<br><br><i>It's as if <u>dark souls and jump king</u> had a baby-</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/90829c98043313b97ade679133f3c321.avif?t=1719328299\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><strong>-True precision platforming!</strong><br>The path forward is up, and your toughest opponents are the <u>bosses</u>. Each jump is filled with tension; one mistake could mean a long fall, and you'll have to climb back up on your own.<br><br><strong>-The longer you hold the further you jump!</strong><br>It may seem simple, but mastering it will take practice.<br><br><strong>-Think before you jump!</strong><br>The easiest path isn't always the safest, and once you take off, there's no changing course.<br><br><strong>-Defeating bosses</strong><br>There's a boss guarding each world, defeat their minions and the boss to progress.<br><br><strong>-Combat</strong><br>Use your weapon wisely to slice the enemies in your way.<br><br><strong>-Leveling</strong><br>Through slaughering your foes you will earn several points that you can use to level up your character, focus on damage or create unique builds to help your way through the dangeroud worlds.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The further you get, the longer the way down<br></li><li>All jumps and falls are auto-saved<br></li><li>Difficult but addicting gameplay<br></li><li>Hours of blood boiling intensity</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/9bc035a2a222c9a8ec0fd68b529ac96c.poster.avif?t=1719328299\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/9bc035a2a222c9a8ec0fd68b529ac96c.webm?t=1719328299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/9bc035a2a222c9a8ec0fd68b529ac96c.mp4?t=1719328299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/8214e8ffb9f82a4554df04fe6450b736.poster.avif?t=1719328299\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/8214e8ffb9f82a4554df04fe6450b736.webm?t=1719328299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/8214e8ffb9f82a4554df04fe6450b736.mp4?t=1719328299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/e6d121e4f991f8b29ea53646d7d42348.poster.avif?t=1719328299\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/e6d121e4f991f8b29ea53646d7d42348.webm?t=1719328299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028390/extras/e6d121e4f991f8b29ea53646d7d42348.mp4?t=1719328299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmosphere:</h2>Meet friends, foes and bosses in this unique whimsical world of wonder in your journey to the top.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Several whimsical Characters to meet<br></li><li>Pixel Graphics mixed with dark fantasy<br></li><li>Several unique worlds<br></li><li>Several soundtracks for worlds and bosses</li></ul><br><strong>Hours of mastering the jump has lead up to this, will you make the jump, will you beat the boss, <u>will you become the FALL KNIGHT?</u></strong>",
